# RK9 pairings cache (data/rk9-pairings/) — generated by
# scripts/snapshot/fetch-rk9-pairings.mjs, regenerated on each snapshot
# refresh. Per-Regional files are ~3MB (rounds × pairings × players),
# multiplied across events would balloon the repo. Cache lives outside
# git; the snapshot agent reads from data/rk9-pairings/ locally.
data/rk9-pairings/

# macOS sync-conflict duplicates (iCloud / Dropbox / OneDrive create
# these when they can't reconcile concurrent changes). Catches the
# " 2" suffix pattern so they never enter git status again.
* 2
* 2.*
